taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"993\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Show Taskbar Border option in the TranslucentTB settings.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/show-taskbar-border-option-in-the-translucenttb-settings.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e You should also select the \u0026#34;Open at Boot\u0026#34; option to ensure the \u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/208224/how-to-add-a-program-to-startup-in-windows/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eapp launches automatically when you start your system\u003c/a\u003e. The checkmark indicates that the option is enabled.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"810\" height=\"373\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"TranslucentTB app in the System Tray area.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/translucenttb-app-in-the-system-tray-area-1.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e While TranslucentTB is the best app to make your taskbar transparent, one thing you should always remember is that it\u0026#39;s a third-party application. This means any Windows update might disrupt its functionality and cause issues on your computer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe best way to avoid such situations is to \u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/how-to-update-apps-on-windows-11/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003echeck for any available updates for TranslucentTB\u003c/a\u003e whenever you \u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/748690/how-to-update-windows-11/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003edownload a Windows update\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can do this by opening the Microsoft Store, selecting the \u0026#34;Downloads\u0026#34; option in the left sidebar, and then clicking the \u0026#34;Get Updates\u0026#34; button.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1265\" height=\"320\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Get Updates option in the Microsoft Store.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/get-updates-option-in-the-microsoft-store.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e The Microsoft Store will display updates for all the applications you have installed through it. Download any available updates for TranslucentTB.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you find that the app is causing issues and there\u0026#39;s no update available for it, you can \u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/749585/how-to-uninstall-an-application-on-windows-11/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003euninstall it\u003c/a\u003e until the developers release an update compatible with the \u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/236195/how-to-find-out-which-build-and-version-of-windows-10-you-have/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eWindows version you are using\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt\u0026#39;s been a long time since Microsoft announced it would introduce a transparent taskbar, but the option is still not available. Until then, I\u0026#39;m thankful for third-party developers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
